    <%- include('partials/navbar'); -%>
    <!-- ! Banner -->
    <section class="about-banner banner p-t-100 p-b-100">
      <div class="maxbalk-container banner__container">
        <h1 class="h2 fc-w fw-6">
          Get to Know Maxbalk - Leaders in Pioneering Defense Technologies
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ! Banner -->
    <!-- ! About Section -->
    <section class="p-t-50 p-b-50 about-section">

      <div class="maxbalk-container about-section__container">
        <p class="fc-p p-20 fw-4">
          In the realm ofdefense and security, Maxbalk emerges as a bastion of
          innovation and reliability. Forged in the crucible of technological
          advancement and rigorous industry standards, Maxbalk’s ethos is a
          blend of unwavering dedication and meticulous precision. We are a
          fortress of safety, safeguarding lives with our groundbreaking
          security solutions.
        </p>
        <p class="fc-p p-20 fw-4">
          Our lineage is steeped in a history that honors valor and commitment.
          Each chapter of our story is marked by relentless pursuit of
          excellence and a driving force to advance the standards of protection.
          With a visionary approach, Maxbalk has carved out a positionat the
          forefront of the defense sector, setting new benchmarks for safety and
          design.
        </p>
        <p class="fc-p p-20 fw-4">
          Maxbalk’s strategic foundation is built on exceeding the demanding
          expectations of the defense industry. Our continuous innovation and
          improvement ethos ensure that our offerings not only meet current
          demands but also anticipate future challenges. This proactive
          philosophy is the lifeblood of our research and development efforts,
          leading to revolutionary products that redefine the benchmarks for
          protection and operational efficiency.
        </p>
        <img
          src="/images/about-us.webp"
          loading="eager"
          width="680"
          height="540"
          alt="About Maxbalk"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ! About Section -->

    <!-- ! About Section -->
    <section class="about-us p-t-75 p-b-75">
      <div class="maxbalk-container about-us__container">
        <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-20">
          We are committed to the sanctity of life, integrating this commitment
          into every facet of our product development. From plates that defy the
          most severe threats to transport solutions that guarantee the
          integrity of vital equipment, Maxbalk's portfolio stands as a
          testament to our doctrine of proactive defense.
        </p>
        <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-20">
          Customer-centricity is at the core of our operational philosophy,
          ensuring that each solution is robust and perfectly attuned to our
          customers' needs. Through comprehensive market analysis and responsive
          feedback mechanisms, we tailor our offerings to provide bespoke
          solutions that resonate with the unique requirements of our clients.
        </p>
        <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-20">
          Beyond products, Maxbalk is instrumental in influencing industry
          standards. By engaging with global defense forums and institutions, we
          help sculpt the landscape of security measures. Our role extends
          beyond manufacturing; we are thought leaders dedicated to advancing
          the field of defense and security.
        </p>
        <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-20">
          As we look to the future, Maxbalk remains committed to its global
          presence, strategic partnerships, and an unwavering resolve to serve
          as the vanguard of defense innovation. Our mission is clear: to arm
          the guardians of peace with unmatched security solutions, today and
          tomorrow.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ! About Section -->

    <!-- ! Our Story -->
    <section class="our-story maxbalk-container p-t-75 p-b-75">
      <div class="our-story_container">
        <h2 class="h2 fc-a fw-6">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="fc-p fw-4 p-20">
          Maxbalk's story is a testament to innovation, agility, and commitment
          to defense excellence. Established in 2022, Maxbalk was born from the
          idea of advancing armoring solutions with greater effectiveness and
          efficiency. Recognizing a critical need in the market, we embarked on
          a mission to enhance the safety of those in high-risk environments
          through cutting-edge armoring technology. Our initial focus was on
          armoring plates, designed to offer superior protection with
          unprecedented precision. However, the evolving landscape of defense
          and the unique needs of our clients soon led us to expand our
          expertise into the realm of armored vehicles. We engineered vehicles
          capable of withstanding severe mine blasts, a testament to our design
          prowess and our deep understanding of the challenges faced in modern
          warfare and defense.
        </p>
        <p class="fc-p fw-4 p-20">
          The journey didn't stop there. As we continued to grow and evolve, we
          were approached with a unique challenge: to develop custom durable
          carry cases tailored to the rigorous demands of military operations.
          Rising to the occasion, we designed carry cases that provided
          exceptional protection for military equipment and drones, ensuring
          that sensitive technology could be transported safely, even in the
          harshest of conditions.
        </p>
        <div class="our-story__images">
          <div class="our-story__img-container">
            <img
              width="300"
              height="300"
              loading="lazy"
              src="/images/truck.webp"
              alt="our Story"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="our-story__img-container">
            <img
              width="300"
              height="300"
              loading="lazy"
              src="/images/shield.webp"
              alt="our Story"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="our-story__img-container">
            <img
              width="300"
              height="300"
              loading="lazy"
              src="/images/drone-bag.webp"
              alt="our Story"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="our-story__img-container">
            <img
              width="300"
              height="300"
              loading="lazy"
              src="/images/team-force.webp"
              alt="our Story"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="fc-p fw-4 p-20">
          Today, Maxbalk stands as a comprehensive defense and security
          solutions provider. Our portfolio now encompasses a suite of services
          that cater to a wide range of needs within the defense industry. From
          the development of advanced technology and manufacturing of premium
          defense products to offering expert tech consulting and integrating
          AI/ML into defense solutions, we've grown into a company that does it
          all.
        </p>
        <p class="fc-p fw-4 p-20">
          Our packaging solutions are specially crafted to preserve the
          integrity and functionality of defense equipment, embodying our
          commitment to quality and durability. Whether it's for the defense,
          security, aerospace, industrial automation, or robotics industries,
          Maxbalk has established itself as a trusted partner, capable of
          delivering tailored, high-standard solutions that protect and serve.
          Our story is one of rapid growth, fueled by the passion to provide
          security solutions that not only meet but exceed the expectations of
          those we serve. As we continue to innovate and expand, our commitment
          to protecting those on the front lines remains unwavering. Maxbalk is
          not just our name; it's a promise of security, resilience, and a safer
          future.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ! Our Story -->

    <!-- ! Mission Vision -->
    <section class="industry-solutions --dark-bg p-t-100">
      <div class="industry-solutions__container">
        <div class="industry-solutions__lr-container">
          <span class="red"></span>
          <div class="maxbalk-container industry-solutions__grid">
            <div class="industry-solutions__left-div p-t-100 p-b-100">
              <h2 class="h2 fw-6 fc-w">Mission</h2>
              <p class="p-20 fc-w fw-4">
                Maxbalk's mission is to excel in R&D, becoming a household name
                in defense products and technology development. As the go-to
                team for tech consultancy, we aim to offer an extensive catalog
                of both ready-to-ship and custom-made products and solutions.
                Our dedication spans various applications across multiple
                industries, ensuring versatility, innovation, and reliability in
                every offering. We are committed to advancing the safety and
                efficiency of our clients' operations, solidifying our status as
                a linchpin in the global defense and security sectors.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="industry-solutions__right-div p-t-100 p-b-100">
              <h2 class="h2 fw-6 fc-w">Vision</h2>
              <p class="p-20 fc-w fw-4">
                Maxbalk envisions being the pioneering leader in armoring
                technology and security packaging solutions, excelling in secure
                transportation and a broad spectrum of safety equipment. We aim
                to transcend the boundaries of innovation, serving diverse
                industries across India. Our vision is to embed our footprint in
                both government and private sectors, reinforcing our commitment
                to safeguarding the nation with unparalleled expertise and
                integrity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ! Mission Vision -->

    <!-- ! Core Values -->
    <section class="maxbalk-container core-values p-t-75 p-b-75">
      <h2 class="h2 m-b-20 fc-a fw-6">Core Values</h2>
      <div class="core-value__container">
        <div class="core-value__card">
          <h3 class="fc-w fw-6 h4">Integrity and Ethics</h3>
          <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-18">
            Adhering to the highest standards of moral and ethical conduct.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value__card">
          <h3 class="fc-w fw-6 h4">Quality Excellence</h3>
          <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-18">
            Delivering superior products and services that exceed quality
            expectations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value__card">
          <h3 class="fc-w fw-6 h4">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-18">
            Continuously pursuing groundbreaking technologies and solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value__card">
          <h3 class="fc-w fw-6 h4">Safety and Health</h3>
          <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-18">
            Ensuring the wellbeing of employees, clients, and Communities.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value__card">
          <h3 class="fc-w fw-6 h4">Environmental Responsibility</h3>
          <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-18">
            Committing to sustainable practices & minimizing environmental
            impact.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value__card">
          <h3 class="fc-w fw-6 h4">Trust and Reliability</h3>
          <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-18">
            Building strong, reliable relationships with clients and partners.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value__card">
          <h3 class="fc-w fw-6 h4">Commitment to Compliance</h3>
          <p class="fc-w fw-4 p-18">
            Rigorously following industry standards and regulations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
